{"tid":1757550,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"再接再厲 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-11-26T14:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T14:49:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"849efc85ac53c3456eb03d8d608f532a4f27c70c","tid":1757550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191126/20813343/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191126%2F20813343%2F&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=89770aa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191126%2F20813343%2F&h=71c3db14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191126/20813343/</a><br />\n<br />\n再接再厲 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191126/large/1574670098_266b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191126%2Flarge%2F1574670098_266b.jpg&h=7954e381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本屆區議會選舉大排長龍，投票率71.2%近300萬人投票，香港市民覺醒一票也不能少，對毒娥黑警黑幫勾結的暴虐表示不滿，以實際行動和數字提出訴求──還有，大家積極動員，為那些在反送中逆權抗暴運動中，輕生、被自殺、被浮屍、被濫捕時反人道毒打重傷失去意識、被火車送上大陸下落不明、可能被摘取器官&hellip;&hellip;等，十多歲廿多歲花樣年華抗爭者，繼續走下去，票也聚眾代他們投。<br />\n<br />\n獻世派種票、鐵票、掌心雷、公公婆婆和大陸人一車一車送到投票站的手段仍沿用。還有街角常見派福袋，很好奇福袋是如何獲取？有何手續？裏頭有些什麼？我問過，但負責人警覺，支吾不答，最後還不理，着人把東西搬到另一處，真掃興！<br />\n<br />\n在他區遇到一位久未見面的朋友，她抱着囡囡，說投完票去看醫生，周日看醫生得預約和貴些，但小孩身上手腳出了紅疹，很難受。因為她的居所和附近幼兒園都飽受山埃催淚煙蹂躪，雀鳥貓狗抵抗力弱，或垂危或死亡，小孩嬌貴稚嫩，怎堪警暴毒煙？有些小孩還會流鼻血。她不在百忙中出來投票不甘心！<br />\n<br />\n11.24區選大捷，踢走人渣奴才，但抗爭之路未完，珍惜手中選票，2020立法會選舉，再接再厲。（盡快救出受困理大生！） <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"f26f081e0227e85d9e7273f8fe3dd30ed4ffe817","tid":1757550,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:46:44.000Z","msg":"呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，<br />\n以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DV4MUJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDV4MUJ3.jpg&h=b1f4ed06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10813ad3111a79feac162e83ebd7fba04b02b9f1","tid":1757550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f26f081e0227e85d9e7273f8fe3dd30ed4ffe817","tid":1757550,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:46:44.000Z","msg":"呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，<br />\n以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DV4MUJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDV4MUJ3.jpg&h=b1f4ed06&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}